69a91b50-fee8-431f-b721-03aad43783f0.title: <player>
69a91b50-fee8-431f-b721-03aad43783f0.text: What is that cape you're wearing?

b4cf916d-1425-47ce-8d4d-e82df32f2743.title: Thurgo
b4cf916d-1425-47ce-8d4d-e82df32f2743.text:
It's a Skillcape of Smithing. It shows that I'm a master
blacksmith, but that's only to be expected - after all, my
ancestors were the greatest blacksmiths in dwarven
history.

a4ea4680-65e2-457a-a3f0-97007fd30db0.title: Thurgo
a4ea4680-65e2-457a-a3f0-97007fd30db0.text:
If you ever achieve level 99 Smithing you'll be able to
wear a cape like this, and receive more experience when
smelting gold ore.

options.text: Can you make a special sword for me?
What is that cape you're wearing?

c9dfc485-7f53-4e11-9077-bb74ac219dcc.title: <player>
c9dfc485-7f53-4e11-9077-bb74ac219dcc.text: Can you make a special sword for me?

b936236a-4be3-404e-944f-56f5cd0f529b.title: Thurgo
b936236a-4be3-404e-944f-56f5cd0f529b.text:
Well, after bringing me my favorite food I guess I
should give it a go. What sort of sword is it?

0f76273c-a51d-4080-9c8f-b7469a8c2577.title: <player>
0f76273c-a51d-4080-9c8f-b7469a8c2577.text:
I need you to make a sword for one of Falador's
knights. He had one which was passed down through five
generations, but his squire has lost it.

513b66c8-394f-4265-807c-0a974320a6cf.title: <player>
513b66c8-394f-4265-807c-0a974320a6cf.text: So we need an identical one to replace it.

4fb4b260-698f-4634-802d-356be3f03356.title: Thurgo
4fb4b260-698f-4634-802d-356be3f03356.text:
A knight's sword eh? Well, I'd need to know exactly
how it looked before I could make a new one.

d6b5c4ec-9e1b-403d-bbcd-e5375a5d773b.title: Thurgo
d6b5c4ec-9e1b-403d-bbcd-e5375a5d773b.text:
All the Faladian knights used to have swords with unique
designs according to their position. Could you bring me
a picture or something?

f295fa41-f9cc-4d6d-827b-b7b4587f3a68.title: <player>
f295fa41-f9cc-4d6d-827b-b7b4587f3a68.text: I'll go and ask his squire and see if I can find one.

options.text: Are you an Imcando dwarf? I need a special sword.
Would you like a redberry pie?
What is that cape you're wearing?

4e07cd45-504a-4949-9e53-16aeadee91a3.title: <player>
4e07cd45-504a-4949-9e53-16aeadee91a3.text: Are you an Imcando dwarf? I need a special sword.

0bfd135b-9e30-499d-9fbe-6b83702c6cfd.title: Thurgo
0bfd135b-9e30-499d-9fbe-6b83702c6cfd.text:
I don't talk about that sort of thing anymore.
I'm getting old.

options.text: Would you like a redberry pie?

efdc67d3-0d36-4b9e-b63f-06cdf62f5f13.title: <player>
efdc67d3-0d36-4b9e-b63f-06cdf62f5f13.text: Would you like a redberry pie?

4f83eb68-920a-4096-9b1f-1007de72e7c5.title: Thurgo
4f83eb68-920a-4096-9b1f-1007de72e7c5.text:
I'd never say no to a redberry pie!
We Imcando dwarves love them - they're GREAT!

edad4222-6be3-4206-95e8-461fc8768b9b.text:
You hand over the pie.
Thurgo eats the pie.
Thurgo pats his stomach.

91ff5da4-3f3b-4983-8ef1-2bfeb9ab18b1.title: Thurgo
91ff5da4-3f3b-4983-8ef1-2bfeb9ab18b1.text:
By Guthix! THAT was good pie! Anyone who makes pie
like THAT has got to be alright!

options.text: Are you an Imcando dwarf? I need a special sword.
What is that cape you're wearing?

8bfc4570-81ef-4fa3-9b0b-7df9bb44885f.title: <player>
8bfc4570-81ef-4fa3-9b0b-7df9bb44885f.text: Are you an Imcando dwarf? I need a special sword.

1a6b83ff-7f2e-40f7-a791-cf0706fa9721.title: Thurgo
1a6b83ff-7f2e-40f7-a791-cf0706fa9721.text:
I don't talk about that sort of thing anymore.
I'm getting old.

options.text: What is that cape you're wearing?

6690eb6a-f87b-43a1-af82-b2b427453597.title: Thurgo
6690eb6a-f87b-43a1-af82-b2b427453597.text: Have you got a picture of the sword for me yet?

fffdc104-e46c-4c74-be89-1dda5c0e03e8.title: Thurgo
fffdc104-e46c-4c74-be89-1dda5c0e03e8.text: Well, come back when you do.

options.text: What is that cape you're wearing?

34de13a7-a66f-42e4-9856-24ad12d113b7.title: Thurgo
34de13a7-a66f-42e4-9856-24ad12d113b7.text: Have you got a picture of the sword for me yet?

ddc836ff-eb47-471a-a887-472b0ac49c26.title: <player>
ddc836ff-eb47-471a-a887-472b0ac49c26.text: I have found a picture of the sword I would like you to make.

996b26ca-7f98-49d1-bc4b-7f7998f2f956.text:
You give the portrait to Thurgo.
Thurgo studies the portrait.

583486f0-46b3-4bb2-8af8-58f61ae4271d.title: Thurgo
583486f0-46b3-4bb2-8af8-58f61ae4271d.text: Ok you'll need to get me some stuff for me to make this.

88aab252-cb08-47de-bf53-e00f1dedb41f.title: Thurgo
88aab252-cb08-47de-bf53-e00f1dedb41f.text:
I'll need two Iron bars to make the sword to start with.
I'll also need an ore called blurite.

e339497c-36c0-4a95-bf52-84986720b8b3.title: Thurgo
e339497c-36c0-4a95-bf52-84986720b8b3.text:
It's useless for making actual weapons for fighting with.
But I'll need some as decoration for the hilt.
It is a fairly rare sort of ore.

0eb36408-02df-4a67-b90b-fd7da52c57ba.title: Thurgo
0eb36408-02df-4a67-b90b-fd7da52c57ba.text:
The only place I know where to get it.
Is under this cliff here.
But it is guarded by a very powerful ice giant.

a904109f-2759-481f-bc29-592c7e6c55ab.title: Thurgo
a904109f-2759-481f-bc29-592c7e6c55ab.text:
Most the rocks in that cliff are pretty useless.
Don't contain much of anything.
But there's definitly some blurite in there.

2a97eb8b-c3a4-4909-b422-818bf049c98b.title: Thurgo
2a97eb8b-c3a4-4909-b422-818bf049c98b.text:
You'll need a little bit of mining experience.
To be able to find it.

f8eba98a-e58c-4724-b012-edf5fe62856b.title: <player>
f8eba98a-e58c-4724-b012-edf5fe62856b.text: Ok I'll go and find them.

c6ca058e-5bbf-4397-869d-04b7600d0181.title: Thurgo
c6ca058e-5bbf-4397-869d-04b7600d0181.text: How are you doing finding sword materials?

86f27261-83a5-4f7a-b438-1fbc63f1664b.title: Thurgo
86f27261-83a5-4f7a-b438-1fbc63f1664b.text:
Well come back when you do.
 Remember I need blurite ore and two iron bars.

options.text: Can you make that replacement sword now?
What is that cape you're wearing?

2f040824-bf36-496c-8051-d1abed4e8c2e.title: <player>
2f040824-bf36-496c-8051-d1abed4e8c2e.text: Can you make that replacement sword now?

2aefb0e9-2065-462c-8eeb-824e2cb8dee8.title: Thurgo
2aefb0e9-2065-462c-8eeb-824e2cb8dee8.text: How are you doing finding those sword materials?

4d958a5f-139e-464d-9634-edfa22d4c87d.text:
You give the blurite ore and iron bars to Thurgo.
Thurgo makes you a sword.

82e3023d-8efa-4454-8183-61ae56aecd74.title: Thurgo
82e3023d-8efa-4454-8183-61ae56aecd74.text: Just remember to call in with more pie some time!

options.text: Thanks for making that sword for me!
What is that cape you're wearing?

b7d5a541-e6ea-4990-b094-c16d1fd31b10.title: <player>
b7d5a541-e6ea-4990-b094-c16d1fd31b10.text: Thanks for making that sword for me!

eac6698e-3c89-4f68-8158-44ac9fc33354.title: Thurgo
eac6698e-3c89-4f68-8158-44ac9fc33354.text: You're welcome - thanks for the pie!

options.text: Can you make me another of Sir Vyvin's swords?
What is that cape you're wearing?

d024ba96-4c77-4f5e-91b0-b7c0b73c50b5.title: <player>
d024ba96-4c77-4f5e-91b0-b7c0b73c50b5.text: Can you make me another of Sir Vyvin's swords?

9e1a4fee-dc61-41df-b9e7-42d8df2f9c97.title: Thurgo
9e1a4fee-dc61-41df-b9e7-42d8df2f9c97.text:
You want that knight's sword again? I suppose you brought
me a lovely pie, so I don't mind. I'll need a blurite
 ore and two iron bars, like before.

57cd9643-b03a-4485-8681-e3ea18510d5a.text:
You give the blurite ore and iron bars to Thurgo.
Thurgo makes you a sword.

0bb3d71b-c808-448a-8b3d-090c25d4ca1e.title: Thurgo
0bb3d71b-c808-448a-8b3d-090c25d4ca1e.text: Just remember to call in with more pie some time!
